{"tid":1760453,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"68% 美國人認為，即使得罪中國，也要支持香港民主運動","createTime":"2019-11-28T08:26:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-28T10:17:41.000Z","uid":28114,"like":90,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"ede46334bd7ec03e9200602eefd8f60e36903cf4","tid":1760453,"uid":28114,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:26:09.000Z","msg":"🇺🇸 美國最新民情究竟如何？香港終於被列入美國民調內容，而這一切都是林鄭月娥的功勞。根據Ronald Reagan Institute昨天公佈的民調：<br />\n<br />\n1. 68% 美國人認為，即使得罪中國，也要支持香港民主運動（不認同只有14%）<br />\n2. 69% 美國人認為，假如中國對香港武力升級，美國應該對華經濟制裁<br />\n3. 59% 美國人認為，假如中國對香港武力升級，美國應該提供「安全協助」 (Security assistance)<br />\n4. 76% 美國人認為，假如中國入侵台灣，美國應承認台灣獨立<br />\n......<br />\n<br />\n對中國高度批判，已成為美國朝野共識，這是新冷戰時代，後續陸續有來。<br />\n<br />\n(Source) <a href=\"https://www.reaganfoundation.org/media/355269/survey-summary-final.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reaganfoundation.org%2Fmedia%2F355269%2Fsurvey-summary-final.pdf&d=gSA20A4kU26EBUHkB65AtLZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=ea849a65\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.reaganfoundation.org/media/355269/survey-summary-final.pdf</a>"},{"pid":"19d2ce7680ba6c6086166f0c1a80ea10231646a1","tid":1760453,"uid":28114,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:28:02.000Z","msg":"Thank you America <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83b7564f41573e0d84c8aabe1272bf945380a321","tid":1760453,"uid":220701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:31:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0777049dc204aebb3986d855bdb4c906b09c213","tid":1760453,"uid":55425,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:32:43.000Z","msg":"好想幫美圖佬含<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a8fb89349e3998427aa3e27a38a02239eccf0ebf","tid":1760453,"uid":55425,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-28T08:32:55.000Z","msg"